{"tid":1787482,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"守護孩子陳凱興食人血饅頭  陳伯已成condom","createTime":"2019-12-18T03:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T08:55:57.000Z","uid":210083,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"531b9de18acb470eca2b7479576fb4c7fa2b4a94","tid":1787482,"uid":210083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T03:01:29.000Z","msg":"我是守護孩子的義工<br />\n一開始見到陳伯咁大年紀都走出黎前線 <br />\n實在冇辦法 唔行出黎<br />\n其實守護孩子好多前線義工都好好<br />\n真心為年輕人 <br />\n但唔知大家有冇發覺每次衝突現場<br />\n只見守護孩子義工係現場衝<br />\n但永遠見唔到守護孩子傳道人陳凱興<br />\n成日企係手兄的隔離街<br />\n安全就出來囉威 成日推義工向前<br />\n當日佢叫人入理大<br />\n但有事果陣佢第一個走先<br />\n結果有58義工手足比人拉左<br />\n但佢就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我最嬲既係<br />\n陳凱興當日靠陳伯出位<br />\n之後趕陳伯走 自己出位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收左百幾萬捐款<br />\n成日話無人手散錢 但就日日不斷吸錢<br />\n唔夠10萬用係手足身上<br />\n用8萬 請13個手足做平價勞工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後過百萬的家長金成日話無人手派出去，&ldquo;how dare you&ldquo;<br />\n食人血饅頭<br />\n百幾萬捐款 去左邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cq3AHme.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCq3AHme.jpg&h=c33f6e50&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/onaSKzz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FonaSKzz.jpg&h=170efaef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec042e81e50c0c3d485e54eb54a8e5952ad2cebe","tid":1787482,"uid":158888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T03:08:08.000Z","msg":"點樣趕陳伯走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以講多啲"},{"pid":"e40a30ac99e4ffff1d77fa3247a3cd06e20beb0e","tid":1787482,"uid":337341,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T03:14:38.000Z","msg":"多謝你地<br />\n幾乎每次示威和衝突都見到守護孩子的義工<br />\n內部的情況就等其他人出來講多小小"},{"pid":"9252930c8a85c01fb98d556cf6c88925ded539f9","tid":1787482,"uid":336616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T03:15:43.000Z","msg":"detail please"},{"pid":"2c8880d18d703434de622b279ba570ddcb1dcb5d","tid":1787482,"uid":210083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T03:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nfGFTDT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnfGFTDT.jpg&h=24056f24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實係陳伯最近真係好似唔見左咁<br />\n搵到陳伯出黎就會知得一清二楚"},{"pid":"31ee6ab8d0f94417044860c5ea41b30cfa0eff69","tid":1787482,"uid":56444,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T03:35:03.000Z","msg":"次次見到守護孩子都會覺得無隔膜<br />\n真正和勇不分<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edccf0b5873e37346c22348ed310347ed9e941dc","tid":1787482,"uid":158888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2c8880d18d703434de622b279ba570ddcb1dcb5d","tid":1787482,"uid":210083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T03:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nfGFTDT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnfGFTDT.jpg&h=24056f24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實係陳伯最近真係好似唔見左咁<br />\n搵到陳伯出黎就會知得一清二楚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T03:43:39.000Z","msg":"即係你地義工都唔知陳伯去咗邊？<br />\n有冇人可以聯絡到佢<br />\n有冇人問陳凱興啲捐款去咗邊<br />\n佢應該每個月公佈收支狀況"},{"pid":"e761b27ffc28e462d94fc5934ca7356d43527df4","tid":1787482,"uid":210083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T04:02:17.000Z","msg":"自從十月開始 <br />\n每次守護孩子行動都已經見唔到陳伯出現<br />\n有d人話可能陳伯要休息<br />\n但其實陳伯仲繼續堅持緊<br />\n12月先接受完大紀元訪問<br />\n究竟係陳伯要休息 定有人唔想比佢參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都希望可以有多d知情人出黎講<br />\n唔係得我一個講<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8DG8HDd5czY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8DG8HDd5czY&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2BuitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=1c2e448d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8DG8HDd5czY</a><br />\n<br />\n同埋事實係<br />\n真係每次守護孩子出現時<br />\n只見義工 不見陳凱興<br />\n陳凱興最成功就係搞左個次好安全既集會<br />\n令到好多人知佢好似做緊好多野<br />\n而有危險既地方就永遠都見唔到佢個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8355b0ce0ce2579efb792370c21dc07aaaa1ae93","tid":1787482,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T04:22:34.000Z","msg":"搞撚錯呀 打完齋唔要和尚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近好多捐款比佢地 係咪開始心野心紅想吞呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053de9a49cb5c7afdc9ec6d70ad84fdd3aca2cb8","tid":1787482,"uid":229593,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T04:23:26.000Z","msg":"【義款去向？】請「守護孩子，好鄰舍北區教會」陳凱興傳道作出澄清<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1708028\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1708028</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n一早已經提出過<br />\n無奈推唔起post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f953ac44089707ecbf62982ba3febda27fc9f3","tid":1787482,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T04:23:55.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[你今日FC咗未] 全港最大的Fact Check平台已經推出了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776631</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eab148fbf5cd5ef3176531211cf63ed23a66e633","tid":1787482,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T04:24:31.000Z","msg":"守護饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644f26e915b2e16667c6855ddde9cd1622f7305c","tid":1787482,"uid":37135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T04:27:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9958e52e3d05d10526c8e52087ca70a44d98e37","tid":1787482,"uid":293281,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T04:32:02.000Z","msg":"先把事情詳細説清楚，不要隨意話人食人血饅頭，做分化"},{"pid":"6a67349ce720b2c5bf6239f3468798840903e9b9","tid":1787482,"uid":137209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T04:32:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"084fb55922386dd26430afd0436c42cbbcbf68cf","tid":1787482,"uid":227153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T04:33:32.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"062d83e780ce8b1986f51dd7dee0353e216d3f07","tid":1787482,"uid":31911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e9958e52e3d05d10526c8e52087ca70a44d98e37","tid":1787482,"uid":293281,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T04:32:02.000Z","msg":"先把事情詳細説清楚，不要隨意話人食人血饅頭，做分化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T04:39:58.000Z","msg":"啲用字咁大陸既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504a6c5f8a7721fcaf73e4061a32986f514dd4c5","tid":1787482,"uid":210083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T05:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJH7JZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJH7JZ.jpg&h=7f79c35b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nelton lo係教牧關懷團的重要搞手之一<br />\n好多教牧都出聲中<br />\n連教牧都咁公言講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多捐款都係直接入佢手中<br />\n佢根本答不出，邊個管理<br />\n推到陳凱興開過直播live解釋下"},{"pid":"c69a2f498e34b2e548ca423288eb6acc5a7e1b75","tid":1787482,"uid":7353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T05:52:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89f9e729c965bf0f5c90f292085669bde1432991","tid":1787482,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T05:54:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1904e3ed6ebff5680055c1202d5b1cf6b88825c","tid":1787482,"uid":83989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T05:56:02.000Z","msg":"咩事點解而家咁多人食人血饅頭 好有雨傘後期感覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"997cc3c0732ec3182ba922d9b866e3c960913bcf","tid":1787482,"uid":43556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c8880d18d703434de622b279ba570ddcb1dcb5d","tid":1787482,"uid":210083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T03:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nfGFTDT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnfGFTDT.jpg&h=24056f24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實係陳伯最近真係好似唔見左咁<br />\n搵到陳伯出黎就會知得一清二楚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T05:57:27.000Z","msg":"周同學出殯有見陳伯"},{"pid":"2fff2a937b50f42a0a6a97511101bbba1c998428","tid":1787482,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T06:01:24.000Z","msg":"仲賤撚過612人血饅頭基金"},{"pid":"f415e6ae0f6b71deb21121b152656de31516a2fd","tid":1787482,"uid":229593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"504a6c5f8a7721fcaf73e4061a32986f514dd4c5","tid":1787482,"uid":210083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T05:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJH7JZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJH7JZ.jpg&h=7f79c35b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nelton lo係教牧關懷團的重要搞手之一<br />\n好多教牧都出聲中<br />\n連教牧都咁公言講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多捐款都係直接入佢手中<br />\n佢根本答不出，邊個管理<br />\n推到陳凱興開過直播live解釋下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:35:10.000Z","msg":"推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f0173a3277dda09e7206d5bab9245da836f568","tid":1787482,"uid":236414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:44:21.000Z","msg":"唔評價其他，但咩叫&quot;用8萬請13個手足做平價勞工&quot;？<br />\n你知唔知呢13位手足好多都係半職？<br />\n半職黎講，平均每人6000一個月已經好好，有啲只係負責幫細路配對嘅工作<br />\n<br />\n話人人血饅頭之前，係咪應該要做多啲功課？"}]}